Package: TreeHeatmap
Type: Package
Title: A package to plot heatmaps at different levels of a tree
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ruizhu", "Huang", email = "ruizhuRH@gmail.com",
                    role = c("aut"), 
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3285-1945")),
             person("Charlotte", "Soneson", 
                    email = "charlottesoneson@gmail.com",
                    role = c("cre"), 
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3833-2169")))
Description: This package allows users to align heatmaps to nodes of a tree. 
    It also provides annotation functions that have similar syntax to ggplot2 
    to annotate rows or columns of the heatmap.
Dependends:
    R (>= 4.3.0)
